The Telegraph - Calcutta : Nation

 Criminal code

 New Delhi, Aug. 2 (PTI): The Centre will tomorrow take up the proposed amendments to the Criminal Procedure Code to tackle the problem of witnesses turning hostile.

 The amendments relate to clauses on witness protection and allowing victims to take up cases registered by police or other state agencies. 




